{"comments":"ObjectFit — How replaced content (images, videos) fits within its container.\n\n## Design Philosophy\n\nObjectFit defines the behavior when content has a different aspect ratio\nthan its container. This is a bounded enum (5 values) that maps directly\nto CSS object-fit.\n\n## Values\n\n| Value     | Behavior                                       |\n|-----------|------------------------------------------------|\n| Fill      | Stretch to fill container (distorts aspect)    |\n| Contain   | Scale to fit inside, maintaining aspect ratio  |\n| Cover     | Scale to cover container, clipping overflow    |\n| None      | No scaling, content at natural size            |\n| ScaleDown | Like None, but shrink if larger than container |\n\n## Use Cases\n\n- **Fill**: Background images where distortion is acceptable\n- **Contain**: Product images, thumbnails\n- **Cover**: Hero images, avatars, backgrounds\n- **None**: Icons at fixed size, pixel art\n- **ScaleDown**: Responsive images that shouldn't upscale\n\n## At Billion-Agent Scale\n\nObjectFit is a bounded enum (5 values). Agents can enumerate all possibilities.\nNo strings, no invalid states.\n","declarations":[{"children":[{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[75,9],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Dimension/ObjectFit.purs","start":[75,3]},"title":"Fill"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[76,12],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Dimension/ObjectFit.purs","start":[76,3]},"title":"Contain"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[77,10],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Dimension/ObjectFit.purs","start":[77,3]},"title":"Cover"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[78,9],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Dimension/ObjectFit.purs","start":[78,3]},"title":"None"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[79,14],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Dimension/ObjectFit.purs","start":[79,3]},"title":"ScaleDown"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Eq"],"Eq"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Dimension","ObjectFit"],"ObjectFit"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[81,44],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Dimension/ObjectFit.purs","start":[81,1]},"title":"eqObjectFit"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Ord"],"Ord"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Dimension","ObjectFit"],"ObjectFit"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[82,46],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Dimension/ObjectFit.purs","start":[82,1]},"title":"ordObjectFit"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Show"],"Show"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Dimension","ObjectFit"],"ObjectFit"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[89,43],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Dimension/ObjectFit.purs","start":[84,1]},"title":"showObjectFit"}],"comments":"How replaced content fits within its container.\n\nA bounded enum with exactly 5 values, matching CSS object-fit.\n","info":{"dataDeclType":"data","declType":"data","roles":[],"typeArguments":[]},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[79,14],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Dimension/ObjectFit.purs","start":[74,1]},"title":"ObjectFit"},{"children":[],"comments":"Does this fit mode maintain the content's aspect ratio?\n\nAll modes except Fill maintain aspect ratio.\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Dimension","ObjectFit"],"ObjectFit"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Boolean"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[98,45],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Dimension/ObjectFit.purs","start":[98,1]},"title":"maintainsAspectRatio"},{"children":[],"comments":"Can this fit mode clip (hide) parts of the content?\n\nCover mode clips overflow. None and ScaleDown can clip if content\nis larger than container and object-position isn't adjusted.\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Dimension","ObjectFit"],"ObjectFit"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Boolean"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[106,32],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Dimension/ObjectFit.purs","start":[106,1]},"title":"canClip"},{"children":[],"comments":"Can this fit mode distort the content?\n\nOnly Fill distorts (stretches) content.\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Dimension","ObjectFit"],"ObjectFit"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Boolean"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[115,35],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Dimension/ObjectFit.purs","start":[115,1]},"title":"canDistort"},{"children":[],"comments